{{作品名稱|name=''2 Guns''|hk=孖Gun雙雄|tw=2槍斃命|cn=双龙出手}}是一部2013年美国喜剧动作片，[[冰岛|冰岛]]导演[[巴塔萨·科马库|巴塔萨·科马库]]执导，[[丹泽尔·华盛顿|丹泽尔·华盛顿]]和[[马克·沃尔伯格|马克·沃尔伯格]]主演<ref name ="notes">{{cite web| url = http://www.2guns.net/pdf/2GUNScastCrew.pdf| title = Production notes| publisher = [[Universal_Studios|Universal Studios]]| accessdate = August 3, 2013| archive-date = 2013-08-09| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130809071134/http://www.2guns.net/pdf/2GUNScastCrew.pdf| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。根据 Steven Grant 所著的同名[[漫画|漫画]]改编而成，美国于2013年8月2日上映<ref name="ComicBook, Kick-Ass 2, 2 Guns Get New Release Dates; R.I.P.D. Holds Firm in 3D">{{cite web | url=http://comicbook.com/blog/2013/02/28/kick-ass-2-2-guns-get-new-release-dates-r-i-p-d-holds-firm-in-3d/ | title=ComicBook, Kick-Ass 2, 2 Guns Get New Release Dates; R.I.P.D. Holds Firm in 3D | accessdate=March 26, 2013 | archive-date=2013-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130303024150/http://comicbook.com/blog/2013/02/28/kick-ass-2-2-guns-get-new-release-dates-r-i-p-d-holds-firm-in-3d/ | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

